<P>(2)反应原理如下图所示：<BR><IMG style="WIDTH: 429px; HEIGHT: 180px; VERTICAL-ALIGN: middle" src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/knowlageEx/05/20140103/2014010317205434335013.png"></P></div></li></ul></div><div class="q_bot" style="display:none"  id="secInfo_554"><div class="secinfo">考点名称：<span class="secname">玻璃、陶瓷、水泥</span></div><ul class="quesExtra"><li><div class="splitline"></div><div  class="notes"><P><STRONG>传统无机非金属材料：</STRONG></P>
<P>
<TABLE style="BORDER-BOTTOM-STYLE: solid; BORDER-RIGHT-STYLE: solid; BORDER-COLLAPSE: collapse; BORDER-TOP-STYLE: solid; BORDER-LEFT-STYLE: solid; WORD-BREAK: break-all" border=1 cellSpacing=0 borderColor=infotext cellPadding=0 width=600 bgColor=highlighttext>
